FBIS4-41900 "drsov125_d_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-125 Daily Report 28 Jun 1994 Regional Affairs Dudayev Oversees Military Command Exercises Dudayev Oversees Military Command Exercises LD2806134694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1046 GMT 28 Jun 94 LD2806134694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [Text] Moscow, 28 Jun -- Command and staff exercises have commenced today in the Chechnen Republic in accordance with the plan for military training in switching armed forces from a peaceful footing to martial law. A report by the CHECHENPRESS information agency received by ITAR-TASS says that General Dzhokhar Dudayev, Commander-in-Chief of the country's armed forces, is commanding the exercises.
